donwload from svn:
     svn co https://linuxplayer.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/linuxplayer/trunk

Dependencies
     kdelibs5-dev
     qmake (qt4-qmake)
     libtag
     libtag-extras
     libqt4-dev
     libphonon-dev
     kdelibs 
     kdelibs-dev (kdelibs5-dev)

to install run
     sudo ./install.sh